{"tid":2203532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「補習名校」教材疑涉黃遭投訴","createTime":"2020-09-15T11:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T12:37:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b02e8c32dc36d14ee73960f2ecb4761ea8118270","tid":2203532,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0915/U633P22T1D851129F1DT20200915180718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2020%2F0915%2FU633P22T1D851129F1DT20200915180718.jpg&h=8cefdbac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　近日，臉書專頁&ldquo;灣區教育家長聯會&rdquo;分享了一張家長的爆料圖片。據圖片顯示，香港補習名校&mdash;&mdash;遵理一位名叫Kenneth Lau的教師的教學筆記上，赫然列著一篇名為&ldquo;We Are Hongkongers，Nothing More(我們是香港人，僅此而已)&rdquo;的英文範文。<br />\n<br />\n　　在這篇所謂的範文中，中國內地人的形象被&ldquo;醜化&rdquo;，香港人則被強調應該僅認為自己是香港人，&ldquo;而非中國人&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n範文聲稱，&ldquo;有些人說我們(香港人)生在中國，我們是中國人&hellip;&hellip;但&lsquo;中國人&rsquo;這個稱呼也會反映我們的道德水平&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n　　範文宣稱，&ldquo;近十年在中國爆發的醜聞把中國人的形象玷汙了&rdquo;。接著，為了論證其論點，該範文列舉了數年前，在內地爆發的有關食品安全的醜聞，並在&ldquo;無證無據&rdquo;的情況下，&ldquo;斷定&rdquo;內地人是亞洲地區從事非法下載次數最多的人。<br />\n<br />\n　　更過分的是，該篇範文還用&ldquo;歧視性的詞語&rdquo;形容內地人，指&ldquo;即便在今時今日，他們還被描繪成是侵占我們土地的蝗蟲&rdquo;，並&ldquo;指責&rdquo;內地人&ldquo;掃光了(香港的)物資、濫用(香港的)醫療資源&rdquo; 等。<br />\n<br />\n　　在範文的右邊，該名&ldquo;黃師&rdquo;似乎&ldquo;意猶未盡&rdquo;，又用中文&ldquo;闡述&rdquo;了段落大意。他寫道，&ldquo;如果自稱中國人，等於承認我們的行為和他們(指內地人)一樣。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　一篇對內地的印象還停留在10多年前，且充斥著歧視性和偏見性論調的文章一出，隨即引發不少港人不滿！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2020/0915/U633P22DT20200915180517.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2020%2F0915%2FU633P22DT20200915180517.png&h=d78d291f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2020/0915/U633P22DT20200915180527.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2020%2F0915%2FU633P22DT20200915180527.png&h=ee0015da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（香港新聞網）<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0915/851129.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"9b688ac167214b6129f69463cca6df6bfeab093c","tid":2203532,"uid":263261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:42:32.000Z","msg":"藍絲on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac52fc59f1634b225a2ef29263fcd1370f37a7dc","tid":2203532,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b688ac167214b6129f69463cca6df6bfeab093c","tid":2203532,"uid":263261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:42:32.000Z","msg":"藍絲on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"全身G點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540e5b7d6eba36b047269b38d2269e33c3613cd4","tid":2203532,"uid":43178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"成版都係英文引號，睇到好頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1361c57697560136b71b6f9249356a28ee2b832","tid":2203532,"uid":303650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"玻璃碎成地都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489ef218dc0d81cd1129bb20481470bcc60dde9d","tid":2203532,"uid":67816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:51:09.000Z","msg":"灣區教育家長聯會<br />\n香港補習老師關你撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f2dbe552fc8c2b138b4c43d61aa7e44a869f39","tid":2203532,"uid":269481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"藍屍咁唔鍾意咪唔好去補囉，又冇人逼你地俾錢，個仔/女肥撚咗唔好喊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=